  "data": [
    [
      [
        "NO"
      ],
      [
        "I arrive at school, and take a deep breath after having such an exciting morning."
      ],
      [
        "Although I wasn’t that excited about sitting in class, programming all day long."
      ],
      [
        "I sit in my usual spot and look out the window. The sky is blue and clear."
      ],
      [
        "I look down and there’s a couple being all lovey dovey on a bench… "
      ],
      [
        "My mind thinks about [Paul]... For some reason, [he]'s all I can think about."
      ],
      [
        "I really enjoyed our conversation and would really like to hang out with him someday."
      ],
      [
        "Maybe I'll send [him] a message later, asking if [he] wants to play with me or something."
      ],
      [
        "In an instant, I hear a voice in the hall that sounds oddly familiar. "
      ],
      [
        "I go out and peek my head to see who it is."
      ],
      [
        "Dude, this is broken… I’d watch a tutorial about rigging before tweaking with this model any further."
      ],
      [
        "It is [Paul]!"
      ],
      [
        "and [he] is giving advice to a freshman."
      ],
      [
        "I wait for [him] to finish, and I tap [his] shoulder."
      ],
      [
        "[he] turns around and stumbles backwards a little bit."
      ],
      [
        "[tn]?! What are you doing here? Do you study here too?"
      ],
      [
        "I was about to ask you the same thing! What are you studying? "
      ],
      [
        "Game design and engineering, how about you? "
      ],
      [
        "Same!!! What?!?!? and don’t tell me this is your class? "
      ],
      [
        "Yup! What a pleasant surprise."
      ],
      [
        "We both enter the classroom and [he] follows me to my seat."
      ],
      [
        "Ohh, so you’re the one who always sits alone."
      ],
      [
        "Yeah… but I enjoy the solitude, so, don’t worry!"
      ],
      [
        "Oh, so, I guess it's better if I stay where I am? "
      ],
      [
        "N-no! I mean.. of course you can sit next to me! I’m uh.. It’s okay, the seat is free anyways."
      ],
      [
        "Sweet! lemme get my things then."
      ],
      [
        "Sure!"
      ],
      [
        "Boy, I almost blew it… but on the positive side, I’ll get to know [Fabian] way better!"
      ],
      [
        "[Paul] soon after sat on top of the table next to me and got [his] handheld console out."
      ],
      [
        "[He] promptly pulled out a controller and handed it out to me. "
      ],
      [
        "Hey, wanna play some games while we wait for the class to start? "
      ],
      [
        "Of course! I’d love to."
      ],
      [
        "We sit and start playing. It was exciting to play alongside [him],"
      ],
      [
        "since I could tell [he] took games seriously, but tried to keep [his] cool."
      ],
      [
        "[He] even had [his] tongue out while playing. That was kinda adorable. "
      ],
      [
        "Unluckily for me, as I was distracted looking at [Paul]'s face, [he] took advantage of it and won the match."
      ],
      [
        "I just look at the screen with my mouth open wide."
      ],
      [
        "Aww, bad luck. But hey, that was fun!"
      ],
      [
        "Yeah!! let’s play again!"
      ],
      [
        "Unfortunately, the school bell rang."
      ],
      [
        "[Paul] sits correctly on [his] chair and I just throw my head back."
      ],
      [
        "Ready to feel the tiredness of coding without an end."
      ],
      [
        "But it wasn’t anything like that. With [Paul] by my side, everything felt easier."
      ],
      [
        "[He] helped me so much with what I couldn’t understand, and I gave [him] ideas to help make [his] project even cooler."
      ],
      [
        "By the end of the class, we both showed our projects to the teacher and got an A +!!! "
      ],
      [
        "I looked at [Paul], and [he] smiled at me."
      ],
      [
        "I couldn’t stop looking at [him]. "
      ],
      [
        "Something about that messy hair and gentle eyes hidden behind those black glasses made my heart skip a beat."
      ],
      [
        "Um… you okay? you suddenly froze on me. Error 404, [tn] not found? haha. "
      ],
      [
        "Ah, sorry! I was just thinking about um… the upcoming projects. "
      ],
      [
        "I see, you think ahead of time. I like that! "
      ],
      [
        "What is this? Do I like [Paul]?"
      ],
      [
        "Nah, it must be my imagination.. yeah."
      ],
      [
        "We just hung out, and had a great time. That's all!"
      ],
      [
        "I slightly shake my head to re-focus, but [Paul] tugs my shirt slightly,"
      ],
      [
        "making me turn and face [him]. "
      ],
      [
        "Hey, [tn]… I’m kinda free right now, and…"
      ],
      [
        "W- would you like to… I dunno… hang out?"
      ],
      [
        "A faint blush tints [Paul]'s cheeks, making [him] look adorable,"
      ],
      [
        "especially seeing how nervous [he] was."
      ],
      [
        "Sure! How about we go to the park? "
      ],
      [
        "Okay, let's go! "
      ],
      [
        "We both walked to the park happily and chit chatted for a bit."
      ],
      [
        "Turns out [Paul] had a lot of stories to tell when [he] got comfortable."
      ],
      [
        "After talking for a while, we sat down at a bench and kept on enjoying the noon."
      ],
      [
        "Yeah, and that's why I don’t play ranked before 10 anymore…"
      ],
      [
        "Aw shucks, look at the time… I need to go and do my homework."
      ],
      [
        "Woah, you take school very seriously, don’t you? "
      ],
      [
        "Yeah… I mean, I guess I really tend to worry about my future… sorry!"
      ],
      [
        "That surely makes me look like a total nerd, right?"
      ],
      [
        "No, no! It's okay! I mean, I really should look up to you haha!"
      ],
      [
        "I totally like Nerds."
      ],
      [
        "I say the last part not really paying attention to what my comment actually implied, but [Paul] just blushes intensely"
      ],
      [
        "and scratches [his] neck shyly,"
      ],
      [
        "probably taking that as me flirting with [him]."
      ],
      [
        "W-well, I can help you in class if you w-want, hehe."
      ],
      [
        "I G-GOTTA GO, BYE! "
      ],
      [
        "And [Paul] runs out of my sight."
      ],
      [
        "I chuckle and shake my head."
      ],
      [
        "[Paul] Is a bit weird, but also definitely a very fun person to hang out with. "
      ],
      [
        "My heart begins beating faster as I think about the day we had together…"
      ],
      [
        "Something tells me that we’ll spend a lot of time together from now on. "
      ]
    ],
